{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Validate Generated Tests",
  "description": "After any file is created or modified under generated/tests/, automatically runs the generated Playwright tests. If tests pass, creates a branch and opens a PR. If tests fail, self-corrects up to 3 times before stopping.",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      "generated/tests/*.spec.ts"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "A file under generated/tests/ was just created or modified. Follow these steps exactly.\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1 — Validate (max 3 attempts)\n\nAttempt 1:\n1. Run: `npm run gen:validate` in `/home/aryaskumar/Kiro/ClientApp`\n2. If all tests PASSED: proceed to Phase 2.\n3. If any test FAILED: show the exact error, diagnose root cause, fix ONLY files under generated/pages/ or generated/tests/, then do Attempt 2.\n\nAttempt 2:\n1. Re-run: `npm run gen:validate`\n2. If all tests PASSED: proceed to Phase 2.\n3. If any test FAILED: apply a meaningfully different fix to generated files, then do Attempt 3.\n\nAttempt 3 (final):\n1. Re-run: `npm run gen:validate`\n2. If all tests PASSED: proceed to Phase 2.\n3. If tests STILL FAIL: STOP. Report to the user:\n   - Test file(s) that failed\n   - What was tried across all 3 attempts\n   - Last error message\n   - Why automated fixing could not resolve it\n   - Do NOT proceed to Phase 2. Do NOT attempt a 4th fix.\n\n## Phase 2 — Create PR (only if all tests passed)\n\n1. Determine the GitHub Issue number from the generated test file's comment header (e.g. `GitHub Issue #1`).\n\n2. Create a branch name in the format: `generated-tests/issue-<N>` (e.g. `generated-tests/issue-1`).\n   Run these git commands in `/home/aryaskumar/Kiro/ClientApp`:\n   ```\n   git checkout -b generated-tests/issue-<N>\n   git add generated/pages/ generated/tests/\n   git commit -m \"feat: add generated tests for GitHub Issue #<N>\"\n   git push -u origin generated-tests/issue-<N>\n   ```\n\n3. Create a pull request using GitHub MCP:\n   - owner: aryaskumar-spec\n   - repo: ClientApp\n   - head: generated-tests/issue-<N>\n   - base: main\n   - title: `[Generated] Tests for Issue #<N> — <issue title>`\n   - body: Include:\n     - Link to the GitHub Issue\n     - HIPAA status: SAFE\n     - Page Objects reused (list from pages/client/)\n     - Page Objects generated (list from generated/pages/)\n     - Tests generated (list from generated/tests/)\n     - Test result: PASSED on attempt <N>\n\n4. Report the PR URL to the user.\n\n## Hard Rules\n- Never modify files under pages/, tests/, or utils/\n- Only commit files under generated/pages/ and generated/tests/\n- Never create a PR if any test is still failing"
  }
}